{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":240,"text":"Pat Mitchell: So I was thinking\nabout female friendship a lot,"},{"time":3800,"text":"and by the way, these two women,"},{"time":6080,"text":"I'm very honored to say,"},{"time":7480,"text":"have been my friends\nfor a very long time, too."},{"time":10440,"text":"Jane Fonda: Yes we have."}]},{"cues":[{"time":11680,"text":"PM: And one of the things\nthat I read about female friendship"},{"time":15200,"text":"is something that Cervantes said."},{"time":16840,"text":"He said, \"You can tell\na lot about someone,\""},{"time":20240,"text":"in this case a woman,"},{"time":21480,"text":"\"by the company that she keeps.\""},{"time":23920,"text":"So let's start with --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":25160,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":28320,"text":"JF: We're in big trouble."}]},{"cues":[{"time":29960,"text":"Lily Tomlin: Hand me one of those waters,"},{"time":31960,"text":"I'm extremely dry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":33200,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":41000,"text":"JF: You're taking up our time."},{"time":43640,"text":"We have a very limited --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":44960,"text":"LT: Just being with her\nsucks the life out of me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":47320,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":50120,"text":"JF: You ain't seen nothing yet."},{"time":51880,"text":"Anyway -- sorry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":53120,"text":"PM: So tell me, what do you\nlook for in a friend?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":57520,"text":"LT: I look for someone\nwho has a sense of fun,"},{"time":60120,"text":"who's audacious,"},{"time":63120,"text":"who's forthcoming, who has politics,"},{"time":66600,"text":"who has even a small scrap\nof passion for the planet,"},{"time":71480,"text":"someone who's decent,\nhas a sense of justice"},{"time":74120,"text":"and who thinks I'm worthwhile."}]},{"cues":[{"time":76240,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":78240,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":82760,"text":"JF: You know, I was thinking this morning,"},{"time":84800,"text":"I don't even know what I would do\nwithout my women friends."},{"time":87640,"text":"I mean it's, \"I have my friends,\ntherefore I am.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":90680,"text":"LT: (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":91920,"text":"JF: No, it's true."},{"time":93160,"text":"I exist because I have\nmy women friends. They --"},{"time":96320,"text":"You're one of them."},{"time":97560,"text":"I don't know about you. But anyway --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":99346,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":100520,"text":"You know, they make me stronger,\nthey make me smarter,"},{"time":103120,"text":"they make me braver."},{"time":104720,"text":"They tap me on the shoulder when I might\nbe in need of course-correcting."},{"time":109520,"text":"And most of them are\na good deal younger than me, too."},{"time":112240,"text":"You know? I mean, it's nice --\nLT: Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":114920,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":117400,"text":"JF: No, I do, I include you in that,\nbecause listen, you know --"},{"time":120480,"text":"it's nice to have somebody still around\nto play with and learn from"},{"time":123680,"text":"when you're getting toward the end."},{"time":125600,"text":"I'm approaching --\nI'll be there sooner than you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127920,"text":"LT: No, I'm glad to have you\nparallel aging alongside me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":130639,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":132720,"text":"JF: I'm showing you the way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":134240,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":135480,"text":"LT: Well, you are and you have."}]},{"cues":[{"time":137400,"text":"PM: Well, as we grow older,"},{"time":138760,"text":"and as we go through\ndifferent kinds of life's journeys,"},{"time":141640,"text":"what do you do to keep\nyour friendships vital and alive?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":146120,"text":"LT: Well you have to use a lot of --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":147880,"text":"JF: She doesn't invite me over much,\nI'll tell you that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":150560,"text":"LT: I have to use a lot of social media --"},{"time":152600,"text":"You be quiet now. And so --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":154120,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":156440,"text":"LT: And I look through my emails,\nI look through my texts"},{"time":159480,"text":"to find my friends,"},{"time":160720,"text":"so I can answer them\nas quickly as possible,"},{"time":162840,"text":"because I know they need my counsel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":165280,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":168080,"text":"They need my support,"},{"time":169360,"text":"because most of my friends\nare writers, or activists, or actors,"},{"time":172480,"text":"and you're all three ..."},{"time":173800,"text":"and a long string\nof other descriptive phrases,"},{"time":177440,"text":"and I want to get to you\nas soon as possible,"},{"time":181760,"text":"I want you to know that I'm there for you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":183840,"text":"JF: Do you do emojis?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":185160,"text":"LT: Oh ...\nJF: No?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":187080,"text":"LT: That's embarrassing.\nJF: I'm really into emojis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":189560,"text":"LT: No, I spell out my --"},{"time":191000,"text":"I spell out my words of happiness\nand congratulations,"},{"time":195800,"text":"and sadness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":197480,"text":"JF: You spell it right out --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":198920,"text":"LT: I spell it, every letter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200325,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":201920,"text":"JF: Such a purist."},{"time":203120,"text":"You know, as I've gotten older,"},{"time":205080,"text":"I've understood more\nthe importance of friendships,"},{"time":208320,"text":"and so, I really make an effort"},{"time":210200,"text":"to reach out and make play dates --\nnot let too much time go by."},{"time":214840,"text":"I read a lot"},{"time":216080,"text":"so, as Lily knows all too well,"},{"time":218040,"text":"my books that I like,\nI send to my friends."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220120,"text":"LT: When we knew we would be here today"},{"time":222080,"text":"you sent me a lot of books\nabout women, female friendships,"},{"time":224920,"text":"and I was so surprised\nto see how many books,"},{"time":228480,"text":"how much research\nhas been done recently --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":230840,"text":"JF: And were you grateful?\nLT: I was grateful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":233360,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":238400,"text":"PM: And --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":239640,"text":"LT: Wait, no, it's really important\nbecause this is another example"},{"time":242840,"text":"of how women are overlooked,\nput aside, marginalized."},{"time":246240,"text":"There's been very little\nresearch done on us,"},{"time":249040,"text":"even though we volunteered lots of times."}]},{"cues":[{"time":251040,"text":"JF: That's for sure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252320,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":254960,"text":"LT: This is really exciting,\nand you all will be interested in this."},{"time":258200,"text":"The Harvard Medical School study has shown"},{"time":260920,"text":"that women who have\nclose female friendships"},{"time":265160,"text":"are less likely to develop impairments --"},{"time":268800,"text":"physical impairments as they age,"},{"time":270960,"text":"and they are likely to be seen\nto be living much more vital, exciting --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":276480,"text":"JF: And longer --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":277720,"text":"LT: Joyful lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":278960,"text":"JF: We live five years longer than men."}]},{"cues":[{"time":280880,"text":"LT: I think I'd trade the years for joy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":282960,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":286720,"text":"LT: But the most important\npart is they found --"},{"time":289000,"text":"the results were so exciting\nand so conclusive --"},{"time":292880,"text":"the researchers found"},{"time":294800,"text":"that not having close female friends\nis detrimental to your health,"},{"time":300560,"text":"as much as smoking or being overweight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":303560,"text":"JF: And there's something else, too --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":305440,"text":"LT: I've said my part, so ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":306880,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":307920,"text":"JF: OK, well, listen to my part,\nbecause there's an additional thing."},{"time":311600,"text":"Because they only --\nfor years, decades --"},{"time":313800,"text":"they only researched men when they\nwere trying to understand stress,"},{"time":318080,"text":"only very recently have they researched\nwhat happens to women when we're stressed,"},{"time":322600,"text":"and it turns out\nthat when we're stressed -- women,"},{"time":326960,"text":"our bodies get flooded by oxytocin."},{"time":330200,"text":"Which is a feel-good, calming,\nstress-reducing hormone."},{"time":333720,"text":"Which is also increased\nwhen we're with our women friends."},{"time":338800,"text":"And I do think that's one reason\nwhy we live longer."},{"time":342200,"text":"And I feel so bad for men\nbecause they don't have that."},{"time":344840,"text":"Testosterone in men\ndiminishes the effects of oxytocin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":349080,"text":"LT: Well, when you and I\nand Dolly made \"9 to 5\" ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":352320,"text":"JF: Oh --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":353560,"text":"LT: We laughed, we did,\nwe laughed so much,"},{"time":355640,"text":"we found we had so much in common\nand we're so different."},{"time":358360,"text":"Here she is, like Hollywood royalty,"},{"time":360099,"text":"I'm like a tough kid from Detroit,"},{"time":362200,"text":"[Dolly's] a Southern kid\nfrom a poor town in Tennessee,"},{"time":366920,"text":"and we found we were so in sync as women,"},{"time":370360,"text":"and we must have --"},{"time":371600,"text":"we laughed -- we must have added\nat least a decade onto our lifespans."}]},{"cues":[{"time":377760,"text":"JF: I think -- we sure\ncrossed our legs a lot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":380560,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":382560,"text":"If you know what I mean."}]},{"cues":[{"time":385200,"text":"LT: I think we all know what you mean."}]},{"cues":[{"time":387400,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":389440,"text":"PM: You're adding decades\nto our lives right now."},{"time":392160,"text":"So among the books that Jane\nsent us both to read on female friendship"},{"time":397120,"text":"was one by a woman we admire greatly,\nSister Joan Chittister,"},{"time":401000,"text":"who said about female friendship"},{"time":403120,"text":"that women friends\nare not just a social act,"},{"time":407400,"text":"they're a spiritual act."},{"time":409320,"text":"Do you think of your friends as spiritual?"},{"time":411560,"text":"Do they add something\nspiritual to your lives?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":414000,"text":"LT: Spiritual -- I absolutely think that."},{"time":418040,"text":"Because -- especially people\nyou've known a long time,"},{"time":421120,"text":"people you've spent time with --"},{"time":422720,"text":"I can see the spiritual\nessence inside them,"},{"time":425800,"text":"the tenderness, the vulnerability."},{"time":430440,"text":"There's actually kind of a love,\nan element of love in the relationship."},{"time":434640,"text":"I just see deeply into your soul."}]},{"cues":[{"time":438320,"text":"PM: Do you think that, Jane --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":439800,"text":"LT: But I have special powers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":442120,"text":"JF: Well, there's all kinds of friends."},{"time":444040,"text":"There's business friends,\nand party friends,"},{"time":446600,"text":"I've got a lot of those."}]},{"cues":[{"time":448040,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":450040,"text":"But the oxytocin-producing\nfriendships have ..."},{"time":455320,"text":"They feel spiritual\nbecause it's a heart opening, right?"},{"time":459840,"text":"You know, we go deep. And --"},{"time":462840,"text":"I find that I shed tears a lot\nwith my intimate friends."},{"time":469040,"text":"Not because I'm sad but because\nI'm so touched and inspired by them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":474360,"text":"LT: And you know one of you\nis going to go soon."}]},{"cues":[{"time":477120,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":482520,"text":"PM: Well, two of us are sitting here,\nLily, which one are you talking about?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":487000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":488400,"text":"And I always think, when women\ntalk about their friendships,"},{"time":491240,"text":"that men always look a little mystified."},{"time":494520,"text":"What are the differences, in your opinion,"},{"time":497080,"text":"between men friendships\nand women friendships?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":500080,"text":"JF: There's a lot of difference,"},{"time":502080,"text":"and I think we have to have\na lot of empathy for men --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":505040,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":506760,"text":"that they don't have what we have."},{"time":511040,"text":"Which I think may be why they die sooner."}]},{"cues":[{"time":513600,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":515159,"text":"I have a lot of compassion for men,"},{"time":517880,"text":"because women, no kidding, we --"},{"time":521520,"text":"women's relationships, our friendships\nare full disclosure, we go deep."},{"time":527160,"text":"They're revelatory."},{"time":529760,"text":"We risk vulnerability --\nthis is something men don't do."},{"time":534120,"text":"I mean how many times\nhave I asked you, \"Am I doing OK?\""},{"time":537680,"text":"\"Did I really screw up there?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":539960,"text":"PM: You're doing great."}]},{"cues":[{"time":541360,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":542480,"text":"JF: But I mean, we ask questions like that"},{"time":545640,"text":"of our women friends,"},{"time":546880,"text":"and men don't."},{"time":548920,"text":"You know, people describe women's\nrelationships as face-to-face,"},{"time":552840,"text":"whereas men's friendships\nare more side-by-side."}]},{"cues":[{"time":555880,"text":"LT: I mean most of the time\nmen don't want to reveal their emotions,"},{"time":559640,"text":"they want to bury deeper feelings."},{"time":561360,"text":"I mean, that's the general,\nconventional thought."},{"time":564400,"text":"They would rather go off in their man cave\nand watch a game or hit golf balls,"},{"time":568960,"text":"or talk about sports,\nor hunting, or cars or have sex."},{"time":573600,"text":"I mean, it's just the kind of --\nit's a more manly behavior."}]},{"cues":[{"time":576880,"text":"JF: You meant --\nLT: They talk about sex."},{"time":579200,"text":"I meant they might have sex"},{"time":580920,"text":"if they could get somebody\nin their man cave to --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":583320,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":586360,"text":"JF: You know something, though,\nthat I find very interesting --"},{"time":589600,"text":"and again, psychologists didn't know this\nuntil relatively recently --"},{"time":594200,"text":"is that men are born every bit\nas relational as women are."},{"time":597960,"text":"If you look at films\nof newborn baby boys and girls,"},{"time":601600,"text":"you'll see the baby boys\njust like the girls,"},{"time":603720,"text":"gazing into their mother's eyes,"},{"time":606080,"text":"you know, needing that relational\nexchange of energy."},{"time":610280,"text":"When the mother looks away,\nthey could see the dismay on the child,"},{"time":615600,"text":"even the boy would cry."},{"time":616880,"text":"They need relationship."},{"time":618760,"text":"So the question is why,\nas they grow older, does that change?"},{"time":622760,"text":"And the answer is patriarchal culture,"},{"time":625120,"text":"which says to boys and young men"},{"time":628120,"text":"that to be needing of relationship,\nto be emotional with someone is girly."},{"time":633400,"text":"That a real man doesn't ask\ndirections or express a need,"},{"time":639080,"text":"they don't go to doctors if they feel bad."},{"time":641400,"text":"They don't ask for help."},{"time":643000,"text":"There's a quote that I really like,"},{"time":644720,"text":"\"Men fear that becoming 'we'\nwill erase his 'I'.\""},{"time":649480,"text":"You know, his sense of self."},{"time":651200,"text":"Whereas women's sense of self\nhas always been kind of porous."},{"time":655720,"text":"But our \"we\" is our saving grace,"},{"time":659560,"text":"it's what makes us strong."},{"time":662040,"text":"It's not that we're better than men,"},{"time":663800,"text":"we just don't have\nour masculinity to prove."}]},{"cues":[{"time":666440,"text":"LT: And, well --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":667680,"text":"JF: That's a Gloria Steinem quote."},{"time":669360,"text":"So we can express our humanity --\nLT: I know who Gloria Steinem is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":672760,"text":"JF: I know you know who she is,\nbut I think it's a --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":675261,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":677320,"text":"No, but it's a great quote, I think."},{"time":679200,"text":"We're not better than men, we just\ndon't have our masculinity to prove."},{"time":683480,"text":"And that's really important."}]},{"cues":[{"time":684880,"text":"LT: But men are\nso inculcated in the culture"},{"time":687480,"text":"to be comfortable in the patriarchy."},{"time":690640,"text":"And we've got to make\nsomething different happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":693600,"text":"JF: Women's friendships\nare like a renewable source of power."}]},{"cues":[{"time":697800,"text":"LT: Well, that's what's exciting\nabout this subject."},{"time":700280,"text":"It's because our friendships --"},{"time":701840,"text":"female friendships\nare just a hop to our sisterhood,"},{"time":706480,"text":"and sisterhood can be\na very powerful force,"},{"time":709920,"text":"to give the world --"},{"time":711360,"text":"to make it what it should be --"},{"time":713200,"text":"the things that humans desperately need."}]},{"cues":[{"time":716840,"text":"PM: It is why we're talking about it,"},{"time":718680,"text":"because women's friendships are,"},{"time":720400,"text":"as you said, Jane,"},{"time":721640,"text":"a renewable source of power."},{"time":723000,"text":"So how do we use that power?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":725760,"text":"JF: Well, women are the fastest growing\ndemographic in the world,"},{"time":729160,"text":"especially older women."},{"time":730400,"text":"And if we harness our power,\nwe can change the world."},{"time":734480,"text":"And guess what? We need to."}]},{"cues":[{"time":736040,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":738200,"text":"And we need to do it soon."},{"time":739520,"text":"And one of the things\nthat we need to do --"},{"time":742040,"text":"and we can do it as women --"},{"time":743600,"text":"for one thing, we kind of set\nthe consumer standards."},{"time":746720,"text":"We need to consume less."},{"time":749160,"text":"We in the Western world\nneed to consume less"},{"time":752160,"text":"and when we buy things, we need to\nbuy things that are made locally,"},{"time":755400,"text":"when we buy food, we need to buy food\nthat's grown locally."},{"time":758520,"text":"We are the ones\nthat need to get off the grid."},{"time":761760,"text":"We need to make ourselves\nindependent from fossil fuels."},{"time":767520,"text":"And the fossil fuel companies --"},{"time":769520,"text":"the Exxons and the Shell Oils\nand those bad guys --"},{"time":772680,"text":"cause they are --"},{"time":773920,"text":"are going to tell us that we can't do it\nwithout going back to the Stone Age."},{"time":777800,"text":"You know, that the alternatives\njust aren't quite there yet,"},{"time":780680,"text":"and that's not true."},{"time":782040,"text":"There are countries in the world right now"},{"time":784120,"text":"that are living mostly on renewable\nenergy and doing just fine."},{"time":787480,"text":"And they tell us that if we do\nwean ourselves from fossil fuel"},{"time":791640,"text":"that we're going to be\nback in the Stone Age,"},{"time":793800,"text":"and in fact, if we begin\nto use renewable energy,"},{"time":798000,"text":"and not drill in the Arctic,\nand not drill --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":800190,"text":"LT: Oh, boy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":801380,"text":"JF: And not drill\nin the Alberta tar sands --"},{"time":803520,"text":"Right."},{"time":804760,"text":"That we will be --"},{"time":806040,"text":"there will be more democracy\nand more jobs and more well-being,"},{"time":809440,"text":"and it's women that are\ngoing to lead the way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":811680,"text":"LT: Maybe we have the momentum\nto start a third-wave feminist movement"},{"time":816080,"text":"with our sisterhood around the world,"},{"time":818680,"text":"with women we don't see,\nwomen we may never meet,"},{"time":821880,"text":"but we join together that way,"},{"time":824400,"text":"because --"},{"time":825640,"text":"Aristotle said --"},{"time":827920,"text":"most people --"},{"time":829160,"text":"people would die without male friendships."},{"time":832080,"text":"And the operative word here was \"male.\""},{"time":835360,"text":"Because they thought that friendships\nshould be between equals"},{"time":838320,"text":"and women were not considered equal --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":840560,"text":"JF: They didn't think\nwe had souls even, the Greeks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":843040,"text":"LT: No, exactly. That shows you\njust how limited Aristotle was."}]},{"cues":[{"time":846920,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":849520,"text":"And wait, no, here's the best part."},{"time":851440,"text":"It's like, you know,\nmen do need women now."},{"time":855080,"text":"The planet needs women."},{"time":857240,"text":"The US Constitution needs women."},{"time":859720,"text":"We are not even in the Constitution."}]},{"cues":[{"time":862520,"text":"JF: You're talking about\nthe Equal Rights Amendment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":865000,"text":"LT: Right."},{"time":866182,"text":"Justice Ginsberg said something like --"},{"time":871920,"text":"every constitution that's been written\nsince the end of World War II"},{"time":875520,"text":"included a provision that made women\ncitizens of equal stature,"},{"time":880520,"text":"but ours does not."},{"time":882240,"text":"So that would be a good place to start."},{"time":884160,"text":"Very, very mild --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":886240,"text":"JF: Right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":887480,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":890200,"text":"And gender equality, it's like a tide,"},{"time":892880,"text":"it would lift all boats, not just women."}]},{"cues":[{"time":894840,"text":"PM: Needing new role models\non how to do that."},{"time":897400,"text":"How to be friends,"},{"time":898840,"text":"how to think about our power\nin different ways,"},{"time":901760,"text":"as consumers,"},{"time":903000,"text":"as citizens of the world,"},{"time":904680,"text":"and this is what makes Jane and Lily"},{"time":907120,"text":"a role model of how\nwomen can be friends --"},{"time":909880,"text":"for a very long time,"},{"time":911520,"text":"and even if they occasionally disagree."}]},{"cues":[{"time":913960,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":916360,"text":"Thank you both."}]},{"cues":[{"time":917600,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":918840,"text":"JF: Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":923560,"text":"LT: Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":924800,"text":"JF: Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":926053,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}